#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/path.md:25
msgid ""
"`ptool.path.normalize(path)` performs lexical path normalization "
"(processing `.` and `..`)."
msgstr "`ptool.path.normalize(path)` 对路径做纯词法规范化（处理 `.` 和 `..`）。"

