#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/path.md:60
msgid ""
"`ptool.path.relpath(path[, base])` computes a relative path from `base` to "
"`path`."
msgstr "`ptool.path.relpath(path[, base])` 计算从 `base` 指向 `path` 的相对路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/path.md:63
msgid "`path` (string, required): The target path."
msgstr "`path`（string，必填）：目标路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/path.md:64
msgid ""
"`base` (string, optional): The starting directory. If omitted, the current "
"process working directory is used."
msgstr "`base`（string，可选）：起始目录。如果省略，则使用当前进程工作目录。"

