#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/path.md:139
msgid ""
"Path handling in `ptool.path` is purely lexical. It does not check whether "
"paths exist and does not resolve symlinks."
msgstr "`ptool.path` 的路径处理完全是词法级别的。它不会检查路径是否存在，也不会解析 "
"符号链接。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/path.md:141
msgid ""
"None of the interfaces accept empty string arguments. Passing one raises an "
"error."
msgstr "所有接口都不接受空字符串参数，传入会抛出错误。"
